&lt;p&gt;While it is sad to see them discontinued, all old versions we manage to get our hands onto will be preserved on The Internet Archive.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;timeline&quot;&gt;Timeline&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I currently cannot give a proper timeline for the transition, let alone rereleases and updates to take place. Time is needed to review and prepare before any actual work on the code can take place.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you don&#x27;t want to miss further annoucements, stay tuned by subscribing to the &lt;a href=&quot;&#x2F;news&#x2F;general&#x2F;rss-and-atom-feeds-now-available&#x2F;&quot;&gt;RSS or Atom feeds&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; or by joining the Discord server.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thanks to all previous users for your support. See you around for more Dynamotivation projects!&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
